riced and represents real value to  any small business. Safeguarding data, protecting privacy Security-wise, the ThinkPad E15 has got your back—and front. All your  data, including log in details, is encrypted by the discrete Trusted  Platform Module [dTPM] 2.0 chip and you can physically close the webcam  with the ThinkShutter cover. Read more

