ally placed Wi-Fi 5 (802.11ac) wireless antenna with 2x2 MU-MIMO (Multi-User Multiple-Input and Multiple-Output) - which is a standard that offers faster wireless speeds and can handle more wireless devices at once. Flexible Connectivity Two USB Type-C ports for ultra-quick data transfer, video streaming, and battery charging.  The reversible USB 3.1 Type-C connector is the same at both ends and on both sides, so it’s easy to attach. There are also two USB 3.0 Type A ports and a microSD slot. Stay Productive Fast boot times, ease of use, tough security and a long battery life are some of the advantages of Chrome OS. With a boot time of about 8 seconds you’ll start working quicker; the simplified interface makes it easy to learn; integrated malware protection stops viruses in their tracks; and finally an efficient use of power means you can work all day without your power adapter. Read more

